      "source": [
        "# Clase 3.2 - Pydantic y Validacion\n",
        "\n",
        "**Unidad:** 3 - Desarrollo Web con FastAPI  \n",
        "\n",
        "## Objetivos de Aprendizaje\n",
        "\n",
        "- [ ] Crear modelos Pydantic\n",
        "- [ ] Validar datos automaticamente\n",
        "- [ ] Usar tipos personalizados\n",
        "- [ ] Manejar errores de validacion"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "cell-1",
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "!pip install pydantic -q\n",
        "\n",
        "from pydantic import BaseModel, Field, EmailStr, validator\n",
        "from typing import Optional, List\n",
        "from datetime import datetime\n",
        "from enum import Enum"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "cell-2",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## 1. Modelos Pydantic\n",
        "\n",
        "Pydantic permite definir esquemas de datos con validacion automatica."
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "cell-3",
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "class Prioridad(str, Enum):\n",
        "    BAJA = \"baja\"\n",
        "    MEDIA = \"media\"\n",
        "    ALTA = \"alta\"\n",
        "\n",
        "class TareaBase(BaseModel):\n",
        "    \"\"\"Modelo base para Tarea.\"\"\"\n",
        "    titulo: str = Field(..., min_length=3, max_length=100)\n",
        "    descripcion: Optional[str] = Field(None, max_length=500)\n",
        "    prioridad: Prioridad = Prioridad.MEDIA\n",
        "    completada: bool = False\n",
        "\n",
        "class TareaCreate(TareaBase):\n",
        "    \"\"\"Modelo para crear una tarea.\"\"\"\n",
        "    proyecto_id: int\n",
        "\n",
        "class TareaResponse(TareaBase):\n",
        "    \"\"\"Modelo de respuesta con campos adicionales.\"\"\"\n",
        "    id: int\n",
        "    creado_en: datetime\n",
        "\n",
        "    class Config:\n",
        "        from_attributes = True\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Modelos Pydantic definidos\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "cell-4",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## 2. Validacion Automatica"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "cell-5",
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "# Ejemplo valido\n",
        "tarea_valida = TareaBase(\n",
        "    titulo=\"Aprender Pydantic\",\n",
        "    descripcion=\"Estudiar validacion de datos\",\n",
        "    prioridad=Prioridad.ALTA\n",
        ")\n",
        "print(f\"Tarea valida: {tarea_valida}\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Ejemplo invalido (descomentar para ver error)\n",
        "try:\n",
        "    tarea_invalida = TareaBase(titulo=\"AB\")  # Muy corto\n",
        "except Exception as e:\n",
        "    print(f\"Error de validacion: {e}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "cell-6",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## 3. Validadores Personalizados"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "execution_count": null,
      "id": "cell-7",
      "metadata": {},
      "outputs": [],
      "source": [
        "from pydantic import field_validator\n",
        "\n",
        "class Usuario(BaseModel):\n",
        "    username: str = Field(..., min_length=3)\n",
        "    email: EmailStr\n",
        "    edad: Optional[int] = Field(None, ge=0, le=120)\n",
        "\n",
        "    @field_validator('username')\n",
        "    @classmethod\n",
        "    def username_sin_espacios(cls, v):\n",
        "        if ' ' in v:\n",
        "            raise ValueError('Username no puede tener espacios')\n",
        "        return v.lower()\n",
        "\n",
        "# Prueba\n",
        "user = Usuario(username=\"JohnDoe\", email=\"john@example.com\", edad=25)\n",
        "print(f\"Usuario: {user.username}\")"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "id": "cell-8",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "## Resumen\n",
        "\n",
        "| Concepto | Uso |\n",
        "|----------|-----|\n",
        "| BaseModel | Clase base para modelos |\n",
        "| Field | Configurar campos con restricciones |\n",
        "| Optional | Campos opcionales |\",
        "| @field_validator | Validacion personalizada |"
      ]
    }
